<h2 id='fetch-api'>Fetch API</h2><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code>
</code></pre><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code>
</code></pre><pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>
<p>This endpoint retrieves a data from a specified collection.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-2'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET https://*.obto.co/o/recs/&lt;collection_name&gt;?stream=true&amp;project=&lt;fields&gt;&amp;oquery=&lt;db query&gt;</code></p>
<h3 id='url-parameters'>URL Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Value</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>stream</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>The ID of the kitten to retrieve</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>projection</td>
<td></td>
<td>comma seperate list of fields to show</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>oquery</td>
<td></td>
<td>See API Query Builder</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

